    "sigma_rule": "title: SENTINEL APEX — CVE-2026-53915 - JetBrains GoLand Remote Code Execution via Untrusted Project Co\nid: ed973c59-e16c-554d-a9bb-8cd72fe38f03\nstatus: experimental\ndescription: |\n    Detects exploitation attempts related to CVE-2026-53915 (Web Application).\n    Generated by CYBERDUDEBIVASH SENTINEL APEX v166.2.\n    Severity: LOW | Class: RCE\nreferences:\n    - https://intel.cyberdudebivash.com\n    - https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-53915\nauthor: CYBERDUDEBIVASH SENTINEL APEX Detection Engineering\ndate: 2026/06/19\nmodified: 2026/06/19\ntags:\n    - attack.initial_access\nlogsource:\n    category: process_creation\n    product: generic\ndetection:\n    selection_process:\n        CommandLine|contains:\n            - 'cmd.exe /c'\n            - 'powershell -enc'\n            - '/bin/sh -c'\n            - 'wget http'\n            - 'curl http'\n    selection_webshell:\n        Image|endswith:\n            - '\\cmd.exe'\n            - '\\powershell.exe'\n            - '/bash'\n            - '/sh'\n        ParentImage|contains:\n            - 'w3wp.exe'\n            - 'httpd'\n            - 'nginx'\n            - 'apache2'\n            - 'tomcat'\n    condition: selection_process or selection_webshell\nfalsepositives:\n    - Legitimate administrative scripts executing via web server\n    - Deployment automation tools\nlevel: low\n",
